Text: Don't know about false info, but the scanning job on this one has quite a few glitches (e.g. Windows CP -> XP). The in-book test answers are also wrong in several cases. I hadn't gotten through all of it, so there may be some more surprises waiting. Still, most of the content should be usable. OCR is a big plus.
